{
  "stem": "3341.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Still, when I think back now, they were treating us, still, with gloves, the Slovakian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They used slur words-- you dirty Jew, and so on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we were not smacked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were not kicked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were only [NON-ENGLISH], which means we were-- we were treated purposely badly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Like when we worked the whole day, digging the trenches on the mountain slopes, and we came home, because that was 5 or 10 degrees below 0, so very, very severe conditions, we came home hungry, and exhausted.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we have to wait on the yard, and the-- the officer in charge said, all right, now we will show you how you have to be trained.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we had to run around the yard in the garrison-- down, up, down, up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Purposely, we were shown that they are the masters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And when we were half dead, then they said, OK, now you go to the barracks and have your black coffee with a piece of bread or something.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So it was a hardship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "After three weeks of being treated like that, I-- I wasn't very strong fellow, never.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I was a skinny child, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I got a terrible cold one day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they sent-- they marched us from the village where was our headquarter.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We had to march to our working place on the slopes of the mountains and different places.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And after being-- I had a very severe cold.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I didn't feel well enough, and I said to the commander, whoever, that I want to go to the revere, to the doctor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He said, you d-- Jew, you just go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You don't need anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he said, you can have two aspirins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "So I was taking two aspirins.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Happened the second day.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
